02:03:01.000 --> 02:03:08.000
And I feel on this subject, nine out of ten people who find themselves critical of me.

02:03:08.000 --> 02:03:11.000
I feel like the aggrieved child who is misunderstood.

02:03:11.000 --> 02:03:14.000
But that's not a defense.

02:03:14.000 --> 02:03:17.000
Yeah, well, I'm not sure.

02:03:17.000 --> 02:03:24.000
