02:07:57.000 --> 02:08:02.000
which is always, in some sense, search for, can we find more common ground?

02:08:02.000 --> 02:08:05.000
Can we find consensus?

02:08:05.000 --> 02:08:10.000
I'm not ever opposed to as much of that as anybody wants to engage in.

02:08:10.000 --> 02:08:25.000
On the other hand, I don't want to design a system that can't work reasonably

02:08:25.000 --> 02:08:48.000
and come to decisions in a timely way and that don't allow people to choose how much of that further discussion and communication to engage in.

02:08:48.000 --> 02:08:57.000
And I'm also concerned that, here's again, I think there's a bias, if you take a look at progressives and leftists and socialists,

02:08:57.000 --> 02:09:08.000
and then you look at the entire population, how much time the typical leftist wants to spend in meetings and discussions and argumentation,

02:09:08.000 --> 02:09:17.000
compared to what a normal person is willing to put up with, normal people are ready to go fishing after an hour.

02:09:17.000 --> 02:09:20.000
And most leftist will stay till two in the morning.

02:09:20.000 --> 02:09:36.000
So I worry about designing a system that fits our preferences, but predictably not the preferences of a lot of other people who just aren't like us in that way.

02:09:36.000 --> 02:09:50.000
So I am constantly looking for ways to get things done more quickly with less discussion.

02:09:50.000 --> 02:10:06.000
I'm also looking for ways where whatever discussion goes on, there's an agenda for the discussion that somehow has a logic to it that doesn't just end us up with,

02:10:06.000 --> 02:10:18.000
will you think this and I think that, or you feel this and I feel that, because those kinds of discussions can go on until the cows come home.

02:10:18.000 --> 02:10:30.000
And particularly if you set up a decision making process where the decision is going to be made by whoever stays latest in the morning,

02:10:30.000 --> 02:10:41.000
then that I really have a serious objection to. Then that one is where I'm going to stand up on my hind legs and say, no, no, no, no, there's a serious flaw there.

02:10:41.000 --> 02:10:45.000
So those are just some thoughts on this subject.

02:10:45.000 --> 02:11:07.000
